        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#10 · $9-99/MO · BEST ONE-SHOT GENERATION</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Koala AI — Best AI SEO tool for one-click article generation</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For budget-conscious solo operators who want complete articles from a single keyword in under 3 minutes.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Koala generates complete articles — title, outline, headers, body, meta description, and FAQ — from a single keyword in 2-3 minutes. It integrates real-time SERP data during generation and includes built-in SEO features. At $9/mo entry, it's the cheapest tool on this list that produces full articles. The WordPress integration allows direct publishing. Accuracy requires review for regulated industries.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Fastest path to complete articles — 2-3 minutes from keyword to full draft</h4><p>At $9/mo for 15 articles, the cheapest effective output of any tool we tested.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Real-time SERP data integration during generation</h4><p>Articles are built against what's currently ranking, not static training data. More relevant than pure LLM generation.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Direct WordPress publishing and automatic internal linking</h4><p>Publish directly from Koala without CMS copy-paste. Internal linking suggestions reduce manual SEO work.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest limitation: content sounds AI-generated on competitive topics; requires editorial review</h4><p>Koala's output is fast but needs editing before it's competitive on hard keywords. Don't publish without review.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--text-3); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px;"><strong>Pricing:</strong> $9/mo (15 articles) · $25/mo (40 articles) · $49/mo (100+ articles)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-11" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#11 · $39-99/MO · BEST FOR AI SEARCH VISIBILITY</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Writesonic — Best AI SEO tool for tracking AI search mentions</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For brands that want to track where they're mentioned in ChatGPT, Gemini, and Google AI Overviews alongside content generation.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Writesonic's standout feature is AI search visibility tracking — it monitors where your brand appears in AI-generated answers across ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, and Google AI Overviews. As AI search grows, this visibility becomes a new SEO metric. The content generation and WordPress publishing round out the platform, though the optimization scoring is basic compared to Surfer.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Unique AI search visibility tracking — appears in ChatGPT, Gemini, AI Overviews</h4><p>Tracks brand mentions in AI-generated search results. The only tool in this list with this capability built in.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>WordPress publishing and 100+ content templates</h4><p>Broad template library covers blog posts, social content, emails, and more from one subscription.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Auto-generates a month of content from a single input</h4><p>Useful for teams that want a full content calendar draft without building each article from scratch.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest limitation: basic optimization scoring; limited SERP analysis; confusing dual interfaces</h4><p>The AI search tracking is genuinely novel, but the core content optimization features are below Surfer or NeuronWriter.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--text-3); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px;"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (limited) · Individual $39/mo · Standard $79/mo · Professional $99/mo</p>
      </div>
    </div>

